# Joint xGASS & xCOLD GASS catalog used: # The xGASS catalog is publicly available at http://xgass.icrar.org and it was published in Catinella
# The xCOLD GASS catalog is publicly available at http://www.star.ucl.ac.uk/xCOLDGASS and it was published in Saintonge
# This combined catalog uses improved stellar masses from the MPA-JHU catalogue for DR7 available at https://home.strw.leidenuniv.nl/~jarle/SDSS/
# Content of this file:
# ID            .. GASS/xGASS identifier
# z             .. redshift: zHI from C18 for HI detected objects
# lgMstar       .. stellar mass (from MPA-JHU DR7)
# lgMstar_p16   .. 16th percentile of uncertainty of lgMstar
# lgMstar_p84   .. 84th percentile of uncertainty of lgMstar
# lgMstar_C18   .. stellar masses provided in C18
# SFR_case      .. case of UV+MIR SFR calculation provided in C18
# SFR_source    .. source catalog of SFR: from S17 if 'xCOLDGASS'
# SFR           .. SFR in solar masses / year from either S17 (10**LOGSFR_BEST) or from C18 (SFR_best)
Communications Physics: SFR is set to NaN if SFR_censored=True or if SFR_case is neither 1 nor 2

# Joint xGASS & xCOLD GASS catalog used: # e_SFR         .. corresponding 1-sigma uncertainty of the SFR from either S17 (based on LOGSFR_ERR and LOGSFR_BEST)
column3: or provided by a fit if missing

# Joint xGASS & xCOLD GASS catalog used: # SFR_censored  .. flag indicating whether SFR < e_SFR
# SFR_limit     .. set to e_SFR for galaxies with SFR_censored == True
# e_SFR_est     .. flag showing whether errors of SFRs where estimated (instead of given)
# MHI           .. HI masses calculated as described in the Appendix in C18
# e_MHI         .. 1-sigma uncertainty of the HI masses
# MHI_censored  .. flag indicating HI non-detections (HIsrc_x == 4 in C18)
# MHI_limit     .. set to 5 * e_MHI for galaxies with MHI_censored == True
# MH2           .. H2 masses calculated from LCO_COR and XCO_A17 fields in S17
# e_MH2         .. 1-sigma uncertainty of the H2 masses
Communications Physics: propagated observational uncertainty of CO observations (based on LCO_COR and LCO_COR_ERR entries in S17)

# Joint xGASS & xCOLD GASS catalog used: # MH2_censored  .. flag indicating CO non-detections (FLAG_CO == 2 in S17)
# MH2_limit     .. set to 3 * e_MH2 for galaxies with MH2_censored == True
# in_C18        .. if True (False) Galaxy is (not) part of xGASS catalog
# in_S17        .. if True (False) Galaxy is (not) part of xCOLD GASS catalog
ID
